---
layout: post
title: Install Wireguard VPN on Raspberry Pi
date:   2020-02-24 00:00:00 +0200
categories: [linux, raspberry]
---

# Commands
```
sudo su
dnf -y install kernel-headers kernel-devel
dnf -y qrencode wireguard-tools haveged
ip link add dev wg0 type wireguard
ip address add dev wg0 192.168.84.1/24

umask 077
mkdir /etc/wireguard
wg genkey | tee server_private_key | wg pubkey > server_public_key
wg genkey | tee client_private_key | wg pubkey > client_public_key




```

/etc/wireguard/wg0.conf:
```
[Interface]
SaveConfig = true
ListenPort = 53489

[Interface]
Address = 192.168.84.1/24
SaveConfig = true
PrivateKey = /etc/wireguard/vpn-server.priv
ListenPort = 51820

[Peer]
PublicKey = /etc/wireguard/keys/nlandier-mobile.pub
AllowedIPs = 192.168.84.2/24
```

# Sources
* https://github.com/complexorganizations/wireguard-manager
* https://www.ckn.io/blog/2017/11/14/wireguard-vpn-typical-setup/
